                <note rend="inline" type="source">890H.001 Zahir/5: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in France</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Marriner</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1934-07-02T17:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 2, 1934—5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>263. Your 493, June 30, noon. You should forward letter for the consideration of
                    the President and so inform the Afghan Minister.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
